---

<ServicePageDetailed
  title="Our Mercury-Free Approach"
  subtitle="Biocompatible Dentistry That Honors Your Whole Body"
  description="Mercury-free, fluoride-free, BPA-free dentistry at Central Dentist Dallas"
  metaDescription="Mercury-free dentistry at Central Dentist Dallas. Fluoride-free bonding, BPA-free composites, and safe amalgam removal using the SMART protocol since 1981."
  backgroundImage="/images/services/abstract-white-texture.jpg"
>
  <!-- Introduction Section - White Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">
              Dentistry Without Compromise
            </h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">
              Why settle for toxic materials when safer alternatives exist?
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <BlurFade delay={200}>
          <div class="prose max-w-none">
            <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark mb-6">
              At Central Dentist, we've been mercury-free for over 40 years - long before it became trendy.
              But our commitment goes beyond just avoiding mercury. We also refuse to use fluoridated bonding
              materials and BPA-containing composites that most dental practices use every single day.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-50 to-green-50 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
              <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark font-semibold mb-4" style="color: #006786;">
