              </p>
              <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark">
                That's why we choose only the safest, most biocompatible materials - even when it costs more,
                even when it's harder to work with, and even when insurance companies don't understand the difference.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach - Gray Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
